To learn more, please visit www.faa.gov/uas/registrationSwift Stream Z-6CV 4Hz 5-Channel RC Drone with 6-Axis Gyro and 0.3MP Camera, Black:Flies forward and backward, up and down, hovers, turns right and left, strafes right/left and makes 360-degree flipsBuilt-in 6-axis gyro for easy flightBuilt-in 0.3MP (480 x 640) camera with videoRecords up to 7 minutes of videoBuilt-in LED lightsFlight time: up to 7 minutesFlight distance: up to 150'Charge time: up to 90 minutes with full charge indicatorAge range: 14 years and up
